2. Security & Compliance
JWT & HttpOnly Cookies: For the most secure login, store user sessions in protected cookies rather than localStorage.

Rate Limiting: Prevent users from clicking "Resend OTP" 100 times to avoid huge API bills.

3. Feature Improvements (The "Vyapar" Edge)
WhatsApp Catalog Integration: Instead of just tracking sales, allow the AI to read the user's WhatsApp Business Catalog to suggest which product to promote based on stock levels.

Vernacular AI (India Stack): Since you are targeting Indian MSMEs, add Voice-to-Text in Hindi/Marathi/Tamil using OpenAI Whisper API. A merchant should be able to say, "Aaj 10 saree bechi, total 5000 mila" and the AI logs it automatically.


